title: 22 Horror Novels - John Saul
description: John Saul has been a New York Times bestselling author since 1977. He has written 37 thrillers. His books cover the genres of psychological, occult, scientific and paranormal thrillers. John Saul's Blackstone Chronicles was a best selling serialized novel and best selling adventure computer game. Cry for the Strangers was made into a film. He has also written a number of plays and published books under various pseudonyms. He currently lives in both the Pacific Northwest and Hawaii.
